				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Version 0.9.0.3,  Patch offset 0x28842 to 0xEB to disable the edit prohibit.  (Not compatible with older format files though, but still, the protection is completely stupid, if it only checks one thing.)
<br />
<br />Version 0.8.8.8,  patch offset 0x29182 to 0xEB
<br />
<br />Version 0.9.1.4, patch offset 0x293D2 to 0xEB.
<br />
<br />Any other version, search for 0x3E E0 01 00 00 74.  There should only be one instance, if so, replace the with 0x3E E0 01 00 00 EB.
<br />
<br />(This took me less than 5 minutes to crack.)</div>

